emuInput.TitMainTitle: Newly constructed brick ranch house with two picture windows, single attached garage, and screen door with filigree decoration, Aleppo Township
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 15, 1955, pg. 19 reads: "Suburban Ranch Home - In suburban Aleppo Township, about two miles off the Ohio River Boulevard near Dixmont, Jim Adams has started a development of spacious ranch houses. Here is an example of the homes which are available just ten miles from the center of downtown. - Harris Photos."
